{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_07_02",
  "title": "kana 2話 よっしゃ、引っかかった！！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――第二回の収録日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Second Recording Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんはまだスタジオには来てないみたいだな\nこころは学校があるからもう少しかかるはずだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana-san doesn't seem to have arrived at the studio yet.\nKokoro must be taking a bit longer because of school…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.4011562347
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お。お菓子の差し入れが置いてあるな\n星の形のクッキー……これは星見プロへってことかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh. There's a snack left here.\nStar-shaped cookies… I wonder if these are for Hoshimi Pro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.284006859,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_plasticbag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8849.326474300002,
          "startTime": 23.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくだし、先に一ついただこうかな……う！？\nクッキーに、何か異臭のするジャムが挟まってっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I'm here‚ maybe I'll have one first… Ugh!?\nThere's some strange-smelling jam sandwiched in the cookie…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.4333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.0016324361
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "あははははは！！　よっしゃ、引っかかった！！\n中身ドリアンジャムだもん、臭いよね～、辛いよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahahahahaha!! Yes! You fell for it!!\nThe inside is durian jam! It smells bad~‚ and it's spicy~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3016327222,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 133.3336195000001,
          "startTime": 32.1349660556
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "星っぽいイメージのお菓子置いておけば\n絶対手が伸びるだろうと思ったけど、案の定だったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I left out star-themed looking snacks‚\nI thought you would definitely reach for it‚ and you did.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2682993889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.4930839857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "あんたが引っかかるなら、こころも絶対食いつくでしょ\nさっすがkana、頭いい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you fell for it‚ Kokoro will definitely take the bait too.\nAs expected of kana‚ I'm so smart!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6349660556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、俺を実験台にしましたね……？\nあ、協力しろってそういうことですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you use me as a guinea pig…?\nAh‚ is that what you meant by \"cooperate\"?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.2333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.3169163068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーだもん、当然でしょ\nあ。そうだ、こころに言ったら承知しないからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're the manager‚ so of course.\nOh‚ right. If you tell Kokoro‚ I won't let you off the hook.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0489570618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことしたら、さっきのクッキー\nあんたの好物だよって、事務所中に言いふらしてやる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you do that‚ I'll tell everyone that the cookie\nwas your favorite food‚ and spread it throughout the entire office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9156237285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.0547621091
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "あんたにプレゼントするために\nわざわざ取り寄せそうなやつが、何人も思い浮かぶわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To give you a present‚\nI can think of several people who would specially order it for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それは勘弁して下さい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please spare me that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9807936669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.4883218925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（その後、こころも無事に……と言う訳ではないが）\n（見事、星形クッキーの罠に引っかかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（After that‚ Kokoro also‚ well‚ not exactly safely…）\n（She spectacularly fell for the star-shaped cookie trap.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――収録本番",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Actual Recording",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7323810737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 93.939048179
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 93.939048179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、ゲストのお二人も聞いて下さいよ\n今日の収録が始まる前の話なんですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right‚ the two guests‚ please listen to this.\nThis is a story from before today's recording began.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2405446212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "kanaが差し入れに持ってきた面白お菓子を\n収録前に、こころちゃんが知らずに食べちゃいまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The interesting snack that I brought as a gift‚\nKokoro-chan unknowingly ate it before the recording.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9405446212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 109.4141515574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "面白お菓子ってどんなのって？\nそりゃぁ……個性的で刺激的な味？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of interesting snack was it‚ you ask?\nWell… a unique and stimulating flavor‚ perhaps?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.0072112878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 117.1317935785
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "だって美味しいお菓子は『仲毬製菓』さんがくれるもん\nそうそう、この前も発売前の新商品をいただいて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because the delicious snacks are provided by \"Nakamari Confectionery.\"\nThat's right‚ I even received a new product before its release the other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4230322619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 125.6859890462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "柚子胡椒味のお煎餅、めっちゃ美味しかったんですよ\nこれ放送する頃にはもうコンビニに並んでるかな～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Yuzu Pepper flavored rice cracker was so delicious.\nI wonder if this will already be on sale at convenience stores when this airs~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 134.9216350397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（仕返ししながら、スポンサーへの配慮も忘れてないな）\n（こころへの気配りは一切ないけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She didn't forget to be considerate of the sponsor even while taking revenge.）\n（Though there's absolutely no consideration for Kokoro…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.6333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "だからこっちはインパクトで対抗しようと思って\n海外の通販サイトとかブログで探しまくりましたもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I thought I'd fight back with impact.\nI searched tirelessly on overseas mail-order sites and blogs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.3309527557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 150.6784149331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、kanaイチオシのお菓子も置いといたんですよ\n前にラスベガス行った時、ドライフルーツが美味しくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I did leave out a snack that I personally highly recommend.\nWhen I went to Las Vegas before‚ the dried fruit was delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.9976194223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 159.1492768449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "……って、こころちゃんは食べてない？\nありゃ、クッキーの隣にあったのに、気付かなかった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wait‚ Kokoro-chan didn't eat it?\nOh dear‚ it was next to the cookie‚ didn't you notice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.9976194223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 167.3898664954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（あああ、こころの顔が密かに引きつってる）\n（カメラの前では良い子なkanaさんを見習うんだ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Aah‚ Kokoro's face is subtly twitching.）\n（Emulate kana-san‚ the good girl in front of the camera!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.7000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The Next Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.637939215,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1194.4196699000145,
          "startTime": 176.8323588849
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
