    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "さ～て、今日も仕事、仕事っと\n……って、なんか、無駄にくたびれた顔してない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright~‚ time for work‚ work.\n…Wait‚ aren't you making a needlessly tired face?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.7990255516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 185.9317359451
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "こころがkanaさんへの仕返しに、事務所の近くに\n落とし穴仕掛けてるのを、莉央さんに見つかりまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro tried to get revenge on kana-san by setting up a pitfall\nand Rio-san found it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.2333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "で、俺も「ちゃんとこころを監督しとけ」と言われて\n一緒に、莉央さんからお説教を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I was also told to \"properly supervise Kokoro.\"\nSo I ended up getting lectured by Rio-san along with her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 201.1966564977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "あはははは、ご愁傷様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahahahaha‚ my condolences.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.1966564977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.0557494723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "にしても、あいつ、まだ懲りてなかったのかよ\nよっぽど痛い目見ないと分からないみたいだねぇ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ that brat still hasn't learned her lesson?\nShe doesn't seem to get it unless she has a really painful experience…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.2639461042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "け、結局落とし穴には引っかからなかった訳ですし\nもう少し、もう少し穏便にですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ ultimately‚ no one fell into the pitfall.\nPlease be a little more lenient…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.2000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 221.2750467861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、kanaさん、ペン落としましたよ\n代わりに拾いま……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ kana-san‚ you dropped your pen.\nI'll pick it up for you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.0666667938,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_tuf-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 221.2750467861
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ、痛っ！　なんなんですかこのペン！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ ow! What is this pen?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.0040326361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 228.4279555881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
