      "text": "あ、そうそう。これがあるんだった\n何か使えるかなと思って前に買ったのよ、ビリビリペン",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that's right. I had this.\nI bought this shocking pen before‚ thinking it might be useful for something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.640936804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "このペンで驚かせてやるのもいいけど\n本番中とかスタッフに、情けないツラ見られるのもなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Using this pen to surprise her is good‚ but…\nhaving staff see her pathetic face during the actual performance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.440936804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 243.9939642513
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
