      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。莉央か沙季に「こころが落とし物してたから\n代わりに渡しておいて」とか言ってみるのはどう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. How about telling Rio or Saki‚ \"Kokoro dropped something‚\nso please give it to her for me\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.2742701373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-kan021.m4a",
      "text": "こころがこっそり、こーんな危ない物を持ってたと\nあの保護者連中が知ったら……ふふふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If those guardians found out that Kokoro was secretly carrying\nsuch a dangerous item… Hehehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.1076034707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_07_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "それは勘弁してやって下さい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please spare her that…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.1214471743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
