      "text": "何がいいかな～、なんたって冠番組だし\n予算どーんとつけてもらって、派手なことやりたいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What would be good~‚ it is our flagship show‚ after all.\nI want to get a huge budget and do something extravagant.",
        "id": ""
