      "text": "あ、プロデューサーさん。お疲れ様です…………え？\nkanaさんとこころが怒鳴ってて、凄い物音がした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Producer-san. Thank you for your hard work… Huh?\nkana-san and Kokoro were yelling‚ and there was a loud crash?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.0333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
